ent with other hepatotoxic agents, and vice versa.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/20122/', '', 'Fludrocortisone, Fluocinolone acetonide, Hydrocortisone, Prednisolone, Betamethasone, Fluorometholone, Methylprednisolone, Dexamethasone, Salicylic acid, Fluocinolone acetonide, Cortisone, More', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Lamotrigine, Methylphenobarbital, Phenytoin, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, More', 1767369485);
