ith NSAIDs should be closely monitored for hepatotoxicity.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/20156/', '', 'Fluocinolone acetonide, Fluorometholone, Fluocinolone acetonide, Fluorometholone, Chondroitin sulfate, Esomeprazole, Glucosamine, Tolazoline, Dimethyl sulfoxide, Minoxidil, Deoxycholic acid, More', 'Golimumab, Cyclosporine, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, More', 1767369485);
